Usage: setSpecialRouteType [-help]
                           -setType {BLOCKRING BLOCKAGEWIRE BLOCKWIRE COREWIRE DRCFILL FILLWIREOPC FILLWIRE FOLLOWPIN IOWIRE NOTYPE PADRING RING STRIPE}
                           [-stopLayer <Metal_layer>]
                           -stopTypeList {swire_type_list} [-bumpCell <bumpCellList> | -instPin {{inst1 pin1} {inst2 pin2}...}]

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
-bumpCell <bumpCellList>            # name list of bump cells
                                    # (string list, required)
-instPin {{inst1 pin1} {inst2 pin2}...}    # list of inst pins
                                           # (string list, required)
-setType {BLOCKRING BLOCKAGEWIRE BLOCKWIRE COREWIRE DRCFILL FILLWIREOPC FILLWIRE FOLLOWPIN IOWIRE NOTYPE PADRING RING STRIPE}
                                    # specifies wire type to the marked special
                                    # wire (enum, required)
-stopLayer <Metal_layer>            # layer to stop the tracing
                                    # (string, optional)
-stopTypeList {swire_type_list}     # specifies the special-wire types to mark
                                    # (string list, required)